sys_remote_update_set.description: Project Name: ITSM Customization & Process Automation One-line Summary: Automated ITSM processes with SLAs, ACLs, Client Scripts, and REST APIs for improved efficiency. Modules: Incident, Request, Task Tasks: o Configure SLA definitions (e.g., P1 Incident must resolve in 4 hrs). o Implement ACLs so only “Support Group Managers” can update high-priority incidents. o Create a Catalog Client Script that auto-fills “Requested For” with the logged-in user. o Add a UI Policy that hides irrelevant fields unless a specific category is chosen. o Write a Background Script with GlideRecord to mass update priority based on urgency/impact. o Create a Scripted REST API that retrieves all open P1 incidents in JSON format. Deliverable: A working ITSM setup with automation, access control, and APIs. Github Repository URL: https://github.com/anurampalli/ITSM-Customization-Process-Automation
sys_remote_update_set.name: US ServiceNow Customization & Configuration
